# Base URL for API requests. Leave empty to use the Vite dev proxy (/api -> :4000).
#
# In production, the API MUST be served same-origin with this SPA (via a reverse
# proxy), so the better-auth session cookie is first-party and survives — see
# docs/features/auth-and-sessions.md. With that proxy in place, leave this empty
# (requests go to <spa-origin>/api). Pointing it at a different domain will make
# the session cookie third-party and unreliable (Safari ITP / Chrome).
VITE_API_BASE_URL=
